/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入去一定開到花灑最熱，出哂煙周圍洗<br />\n之後再出滴露同洗廁所專用水<br />\n賓周有機會會掂到既地方全部都洗一次<br />\n反而床就冇乜理，訓前沖涼，起身沖涼<br />\n廁所門長開，唔會閂，唔洗掂到門鎖<br />\n<br />\n基本上係咁，電視唔會開，燈制掂完洗手"},{"pid":"6833488b6fe20e897a7eab6ed93f4af2c11fba5d","tid":1119944,"uid":92132,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"ON9 究竟潔辟撚會唔會打茄輪 十萬細菌痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005404f37aeed80dd4ae28f520f9003edb3250d8","tid":1119944,"uid":2687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"我會帶滴露同噴酒精消毒所有嘢，之前試過地板好多塵幫佢拖咗一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友同我一齊去旅行會爭同我同房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbb6b478b3ae35606431f4e9104f50e45180f36","tid":1119944,"uid":61281,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4ee82bf877f88c5094c985be78384a6673bb9bfa","tid":1119944,"uid":79410,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"7e4b13b6b28c420b2c0337dd505aca850f365177","tid":1119944,"uid":228963,"like":151,"dislike":0,"score":151,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"我BOOK 酒店見到係地毯, 我就唔會BOOK 嗰間.<br />\n次次住親酒店係地毯.隻腳都痕到仆街. <br />\n懷疑開張到而家都係未洗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"下，正常人都唔會喺酒店赤腳踩落地掛"},{"pid":"f99443c19b864cdc6740868cbfc07cd98d1189c6","tid":1119944,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"用紫外燈照下塊被有冇精液先"},{"pid":"03674b67909683a97f0fdf132ed5e1f459c0593b","tid":1119944,"uid":201380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"一定唔會用酒店水煲，毛巾會用但內心其實好淆底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他就真係無咩特別去抹，因為旅行通常都淨喺夜晚酒店訓覺，所以好多都用唔到，例如遙控同埋浴缸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d781af9266092a418f7525297cd7b6021e72cc","tid":1119944,"uid":29283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"bf3699a8bacd036e995bea151bd87d139c6a2617","tid":1119944,"uid":150348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬有冇諗過睇醫生"},{"pid":"2bbcba9f75dd67bed11f37ecae26e56551169a9b","tid":1119944,"uid":129235,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8e4ba614c3d13991939da5699c2d572095caa64b","tid":1119944,"uid":215441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"1.入房後用酒精清潔會掂的門柄/按鈕<br />\n2.用拖鞋個膠袋反轉再套住個電視遙控制<br />\n3.煲水洗水煲<br />\n4.用滴露燒毒浴缸<br />\n5.浴袍鋪喺梳化上坐<br />\n<br />\n各位如果仲有好啲嘅建議請指教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"呢位巴打重痴線過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會做既係呢幾樣<br />\n1. 日本藥妝店會有得買d 衣服除臭清潔噴劑，我一落機就會去買支來用，每晚返酒店噴床、枕頭同埋自己d 外套、牛仔褲(因為唔會洗)<br />\n2. 買包大包D 既消毒濕紙巾，然後每晚用濕紙巾抹個電視遙控(因為夜晚個remote 我會放上床睇電視方便轉台)、床頭燈制，同埋每日抹衣架同廁所板<br />\n其他既我好少理<br />\n<br />\n門柄我唔會抹，因為開門出街隻手預污糟，返入來既話直接洗手算<br />\n水煲我唔會用，買支裝水算啦<br />\n浴缸我由佢，因為我唔會浸浴，企係度沖算<br />\n梳化我著住牛仔褲/出街褲坐，所以又係由佢"},{"pid":"280c4feb5759093a316cde6371b44ce4216c1668","tid":1119944,"uid":161126,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"我通常用condom笠全身先入住酒店"},{"pid":"0ed3dbeed7e22064b8f2d8dc6b2fe4b6f642731e","tid":1119944,"uid":61281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"上面係咪傻撚左 幫酒店拖埋地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c648c048172fd87330e5f1af25f8baaa583386c6","tid":1119944,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6833488b6fe20e897a7eab6ed93f4af2c11fba5d","tid":1119944,"uid":92132,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy"